### English Title:
Egyptian Interior Ministry Clarifies Viral Video of Students Signing Informal Marriage Contract

### English Text Summary:
The Egyptian Ministry of Interior has addressed a viral video circulating on social media that claimed a middle school student and a female student signed an informal marriage contract. The ministry clarified that the video was based on false claims made by a woman who was involved in a dispute with school officials while trying to enroll her child. The ministry urged parents to be cautious and confirmed that there were no reports or incidents related to the claims made in the video. Legal actions have been taken against the woman for her false allegations.

